title: The Crossroads Part 1
description: An attempt to use a derelict SpaceBridge sends The Ark to Unspace!

title: Parley Part 1
description: Megatron and Optimus parley in an attempt to unite against Starscream.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: Party Down Part 2
description: A malfunction in Wheeljack's party favors turns most of the Autobot crew feral, leaving Optimus, Cheetor, and Teletraan-X in a race to save their friends.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 2
description: Optimus seemingly sacrifices himself to get the Allspark back from Starscream, leaving the rest of the Autobots to deal with Megatron.

title: Dark Birth Part 1
description: While Starscream acquires new power through the Allspark, the Autobots mistakenly assume Starscream is still under Megatron's command.

title: Ghost Town Part 1
description: When Windblade mysteriously steals the Allspark, Optimus, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor follow her to a strange abandoned city.

title: Secret Science Part 1
description: While studying the scraplets Wheeljack is kidnapped by Shockwave who tries to enlist Wheeljack's help.

title: Perfect Storm Part 2
description: Arcee and Grimlock get an adventure they never bargained for as they protect the helpless Ark from all manner of space anomalies.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: Perfect Storm Part 1
description: Arcee and Grimlock go off on an adventure only to return and discover the Ark without power and their friends all in stand-by mode.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 1
description: The Autobots and Decepticons are surprised by the return of their long-lost comrades, Jetfire and Skybyte.

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: Starscream's Children Part 2
description: Starscream reveals his scraplet army, incapacitating the Autobots and Decepticons and setting up a show down between him and Cheetor.

title: Escape From Earth Part 2
description: With the Ark extricated from Mt. St. Hilary, the Autobots must run the gauntlet of Decepticon forces to escape Earth with the Allspark.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: Parley Part 2
description: The Autobot-Decepticon peace talks breaks down after Slipstream returns with a dire warning.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: Party Down Part 1
description: On their way to back to Cybertron, the Autobots attempt to have some well-deserved fun by throwing a party.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Spotted Part 1
description: Worried about finding a useful position among the Autobots, Cheetor learns how to become an Autobot Scout from Bumblebee.

title: Escape From Earth Part 1
description: Optimus struggles to recover from using the Matrix of Leadership while the Autobots attempt to get the Allspark back to Cybertron.

title: Wiped Out Part 2
description: Separated from his friends, Cheetor is captured by the territorial Sharkticons who enlist him in their fight over the last remaining bits of their destroyed planet.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 2
description: Starscream gives Jetfire and Skybyte Spark Armor to escalate their feud and distract everyone from his machinations.

title: Starscream's Children Part 1
description: The Autobots received a distress call from the Nemesis and must come to the aid of their arch-enemies.

title: The Crossroads Part 2
description: Optimus and the Autobots team up with some very familiar faces to escape Unspace.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 1
description: Starscream successfully merges with the Allspark, spelling doom for the Autobots and Decepticons.

title: Secret Science Part 2
description: Wheeljack attempts to break out of the Nemesis while Windblade hunts down Bludgeon to avenge Slipstream.

title: Ghost Town Part 2
description: Teletraan-X attempts to rehabilitate Starscream while Optimus, Bee, Hot Rod and Cheetor's quest to save Windblade uncovers a city that is more than meets the eye.

title: Wiped Out Part 1
description: Out in space to catch some solar waves, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor discover the asteroid remains of a mysterious planet.

title: Dark Birth Part 2
description: The Autobots and Decepticons battle aboard the Nemesis while Starscream uses the Allspark and Vector Sigma to create new allies.

title: Spotted Part 2
description: Cheetor's scout training with Bee lands them in the clutches of Starscream who tests an evil experiment on them.
